<subSubSection id="2A6D654349BDA87ECF891E30FE36D805" pageId="0" pageNumber="1" type="description">
<paragraph id="AA86C596068C5CBEB994FF07671EE43D" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">Description.</paragraph>
<paragraph id="2DC58EB4AD9493E0E3835ACFFEE6A5AD" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">
Liana to 10 m; stems subtomentose, woody. Leaves petiolate, 3-11 
<normalizedToken id="13F19E42963208F60AFF5000EADDE31B" originalValue="×">x</normalizedToken>
2.5-8 cm, ovate, shortly acuminate, cordate with broad sinus, adaxially green, tomentellous, abaxially grey-tomentose; petioles 1.5-5 cm, tomentellous. Inflorescence of few-flowered axillary cymes, peduncles 2-5.5 cm, white-tomentellous; bracteoles 5-7 mm, oblong-lanceolate, white-tomentellous, tardily deciduous; secondary peduncles up to 1.5 cm; pedicels (5-)15-45 mm, often long and straight, white-tomentose; outer sepals unequal, outer 10-15 
<normalizedToken id="3451DD1A450DF6AD7C23242F7C762D1B" originalValue="×">x</normalizedToken>
6-7 mm, ovate, acute, abruptly narrowed to subtruncate at base, often undulate to fimbriate-margined, white-tomentose, inner sepals 16-17 
<normalizedToken id="3592067277D8CB8AC321117ABD0B1A4C" originalValue="×">x</normalizedToken>
7 mm, broadly oblong, obtuse, tomentellous with broad scarious margins; corolla hypocrateriform, with cylindrical basal tube 3.5-4.5 cm in length and spreading, deep pink, lobes, pilose on the exterior, especially on tube and midpetaline bands, limb 5.5-6 cm diam.; stamens exserted, equal. Capsules 16 
<normalizedToken id="B6CDD9BBEDAAFCEE01F3BE3CD6247645" originalValue="×">x</normalizedToken>
12 mm conical, shortly rostrate, tomentellous; seeds 8-9 
<normalizedToken id="D83668F6B9781E37FDBCA59159D4CCC2" originalValue="×">x</normalizedToken>
5 mm, long-pilose.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
